},{"pid":"08e4745f12e48448b823eac0d48f9a6d536ac8a0","tid":2389302,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T20:07:21.000Z","msg":"殺無赦！"},{"pid":"8d31f0e98611f86ee2a61a9781c1cc3a72d4f75b","tid":2389302,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"Either MI5 or make them disappear yourself.<br />\nYour call."},{"pid":"10f9c81c2f809f17a269e0480fd8dbeabb1a738e","tid":2389302,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 引致百國聯軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>支共無錢發難</ins><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２A：支共無錢發難引致世界大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[軍事小說] 習近平氏の希特拉化！英美德法荷日印澳同盟國形成！普京：依家局勢好似二戰前既30年代！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gCmQrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gCmQrS</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"9f18e422d06ee7229e86048570c72cb6f5a59731","tid":2389302,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T22:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16f02b84a895967493990fea00f4a6e7d77ef0f","tid":2389302,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T22:36:32.000Z","msg":"最近好多5毛狂俾負評<br />\n講句『加油，祝福』都成百個負評"},{"pid":"6cac05b9e13684fec75886167b4245f45362df94","tid":2389302,"uid":24133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f16f02b84a895967493990fea00f4a6e7d77ef0f","tid":2389302,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T22:36:32.000Z","msg":"最近好多5毛狂俾負評<br />\n講句『加油，祝福』都成百個負評"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T22:57:46.000Z","msg":"連狗唔撚做嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb259c7a27f1d0d6299b3e16fe67468dd854df2","tid":2389302,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"28b58f549f86d8e48b62e83a7ccc647b2f82a24c","tid":2389302,"uid":108016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:39:50.000Z","msg":"英 國 舊 移 民 恥 笑 新 移 民 係 曱 甴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2387045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2387045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"970a419d84ad698c1a2aa6ec3a88b4de75a588eb","tid":2389302,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28b58f549f86d8e48b62e83a7ccc647b2f82a24c","tid":2389302,"uid":108016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:39:50.000Z","msg":"英 國 舊 移 民 恥 笑 新 移 民 係 曱 甴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2387045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2387045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T00:09:41.000Z","msg":"就係講緊呢啲<br />\n絕對值得搞<br />\n如果有確實證據就報MI5<br />\n如果想親手處決，